{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Skelter Medooz |image = Skelter Medooz.jpg |caption = Skelter Medooz |category = Normal Minor Enemy<br/ >[[Challenge Battle Enemy (XC3)|Challenge Battle Enemy]] |type = [[Medooz]] |level = 27-28<br/ >70 |area = [[Great Cotte Falls]] ([[Fallfoot Battlescar]]) |spawntime = Anytime<br/ >During ''[[Men! Of! The Sea! IV]]'' |respawn = Yes<br/ >No |movement = Air |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = }} '''Skelter Medoozes''' are Normal Minor Enemies in {{XC3}}. They are members of the [[Medooz]] family, and can be found at level 27-28 at at [[Fallfoot Battlescar]] near the base of the [[Great Cotte Falls]]. One is fought at level 70 during the first wave of the [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] ''[[Men! Of! The Sea! IV]]''.
