{{for|other uses|Skill}} {{spoiler}} '''Skills''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|スキル}}, ''sukiru'') are a battle mechanic in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}.
== Overview == They are unlocked by reaching certain [[Class Rank (XC3)|Class Ranks]] in certain [[Class (XC3)|Classes]]. Ranking up a class earns new [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Arts]] or Skills. {{clr}}
