== {{XC3FR|sub}} == In {{XC3FR|sub}}, skills are acquired by spending Affinity Points in each character's [[Affinity Growth]]. Each character can unlock 4 class skills, which each can be upgraded a maximum of 2 times to increase their effects.
Additionally, each character has an Initiative Effect skill, which grants a certain [[Status Effect|buff]] to the party, or inflicts a combo reaction on the enemy when beginning the battle with an attack from a specified direction.
Each character also has several other skills that cannot be upgraded, but offer stat increases or unique effects.
[[Na'el]] has 4 skills unique to her class, [[War Mage]], but as she does not possess an Affinity Growth, these skills are unlocked immediately, but they cannot be upgraded. She does not posses an Initiative Effect or any unnamed skills either.
