'''Skirmish''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|勢力争い}}, ''Seiryoku arasoi'', lit. power struggle) is a mechanic in {{XC3}}.<ref>https://topics.nintendo.co.jp/article/dec68671-d6ac-4982-abec-93cb91a1dcb4</ref>
== Overview == Occasionally, the party will encounter groups of [[Enemy (XC3)|enemies]], soldiers or monsters, fighting one another in the field. They can choose to join either side of the battle, with each offering different rewards, such as [[Gold]], [[Experience Points (XC3)|Bonus Experience]], [[Affinity (XC3)|Affinity]] with a local colony, or [[Nopon Coin (XC3)|Nopon Coins]]. The strategic key is to determine which reward is better or which battle seems easier to win. However, when the party is helping one group as part of a [[Quest (XC3)|quest]], it is not possible to join the other group. {{clr}}
